<p>One time I was visiting my step son and his wife, his 1 1/2 yr old and himself.. Were all sick with some horrible head cold picked up from daycare (the biggest germfest anywhere). By the time we left my throat was beginning something&#8230; </p>
<p>No echinacea in the house.. Only thing available was an old bottle of rye. </p>
<p>So what is echinacea anyway but alcohol from a flower&#8230; ?</p>
<p>Rye, Meyers lemon, mix, swig</p>
<p>Worked</p>
<p>&#8230;And rye is much cheaper</p>
