<p>The recipe that you posted is identical to the one that I use with one exception that my mom started and I&#39;ve carried on:</p>
<p>Wrap the dough around a Hershey Kiss.</p>
<p>Bake the same way, same temp. It doesn&#39;t melt and OMG! So! Good!</p>
