    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I had to pop in and say Happy New Year. I&#39;m sat here, with a cup of red bush tea and a luscious slice of banana, dark chocolate and ginger cake. Buttered. Is that too indulgent?</p>
    </div>

      </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-42045" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
